events.name: EmployeeCreated
events.description: This event is published by SAP HCM system and triggered based on the driver registration as part of the driver management app within the ACME Rideshare application domain.

applications.name: TransitConverter
applications.description: The TransitConverter microservice is converting the EmployeeCreated event into an object for data transfer. It should be exchanged with cloud services, where different security policies apply. One requirement is that confidential data needs to be encryped before it is transferred to Microsoft Azure Event Hub, independent of having SSL/TLS in place or not. Therefore, HashiCorp Vault is used for encryption, decryption and management of the secrets.
